 * List<ProductDto>
 */
5. transformToDTO()
/******************************************************************************
 * ENTITY TO DTO CONVERSION
 ******************************************************************************

/*
 * Purpose:
 *
 * Converts Product Entity into ProductDto.
 *
 * Why?
 *
 * Entity contains database information.
 *
 * DTO contains only the required information
 * to be sent to the frontend.
 *
 * BeanUtils.copyProperties()
 *
 * Copies matching properties automatically.
 *
 * Example:
 *
 * Product
 * ----------
 * productId
 * name
 * price
 * imageUrl
 *
 * ↓
 *
 * ProductDto
 * ----------
 * productId
 * name
 * price
 * imageUrl
 *
 * Benefits:
 *
 * • Less code
 * • Faster development
 * • Easy maintenance
 */
