/******************************************************************************
 * PRODUCT DTO
 ******************************************************************************

/*
 * DTO = Data Transfer Object
 *
 * Purpose:
 *
 * Transfers data between backend and frontend.
 *
 * Why DTO?
 *
 * • Hide internal database fields.
 * • Improve security.
 * • Reduce unnecessary data transfer.
 * • Separate database model from API model.
 *
 * Flow:
 *
 * Product Entity
 *       │
 *       ▼
 * ProductDto
 *       │
 *       ▼
 * JSON Response
 *       │
 *       ▼
 * React Application
 */
