 * • Development
 * • Unit Testing
 * • Prototype Applications
 *
 * Since H2 runs completely in memory, no external database installation
 * (like MySQL or PostgreSQL) is required.
 *
 * =============================================================================
 * WHY H2 DATABASE?
 * =============================================================================
 *
 * Advantages:
 *
 * ✓ Lightweight
 * ✓ Fast
 * ✓ Easy to configure
 * ✓ No installation required
 * ✓ Embedded inside the application
 * ✓ Ideal for development and testing
 *
 * When the Spring Boot application starts,
 * H2 creates the database automatically.
 *
 * When the application stops,
 * the in-memory database is removed.
 */
